steps.name: go to the site in press login button
fill the fields of email and password by using resources
after login in press the (add) button
while in (addpage) make new contact with generating everything but description
converting the new contact to string and filling the form
after creating new contact gets in (contacts_Page), and checking if the contact is the same as we created AND save
deleting the contact and checking if hes null
